a:t.name: comment
a:t.value: This function returns an interval constructed using the `date from` extractor on the start and end values of the input date-time interval. Note that using a precision specifier such as `day of` as part of a timing phrase is preferred to communicate intent to perform day-level comparison, as well as for general readability.
